{"tid":1823873,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"要人呀！想轉工作環境請入嚟⋯⋯","createTime":"2020-01-14T04:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T13:51:47.000Z","uid":275463,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"535a2c6aa32e379f70696d1a633a182efab08b4e","tid":1823873,"uid":275463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T04:35:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要人呀！有Project唔夠人做，有新諗頭都要有人幫手。</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/00xtWsU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F00xtWsU.jpg&h=1a8c54bb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n我公司從2014年後，再沒有外判程式或系統工作到其他公司或者其他國家了。因為我希望可以同全世界講我公司出品係「100% Made in Hong Kong」。坦白講，咁做係會令自已既營運成本提高左、利潤肯定少左。但係得到既係：可以聚到一班共同理念、齊上齊落既手足/人材，而唔係員工咁簡單。 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">公司簡介：<a href=\"https://www.silvercube.com.hk/about-us/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.silvercube.com.hk%2Fabout-us%2F&d=x7%2Fg1uS4a%2BT3911x%2BwLoHEn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=e3f9f79a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.silvercube.com.hk/about-us/</a></span><br />\n經驗方面我唔係睇得最重，返而能力、責任、溝通先係考慮重點。<br />\n編程技能： PHP, MySQL, HTML, CSS, AJAX, XML, Javascript, APIs Integration (如圖)<br />\n軟技能：Logical Thinking<br />\n如果咁啱你睇到呢個PO、又有曬以上技能、又有興趣試下，希望可以同你聯絡傾多D。<br />\n我既聯絡方法：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/mrsamgor\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmrsamgor&d=x7%2Fg1uS4a%2BT3911x%2BwLoHEn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=b6dddfa0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/mrsamgor</a><br />\n[url]mailto: samuel@silvercube.com.hk[/url]"},{"pid":"63dbea1d4f8572f5338f49983d064e1153fb6565","tid":1823873,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T04:48:09.000Z","msg":"咩價位"},{"pid":"7a75f9a404da4d83985daa56843531b06b420b65","tid":1823873,"uid":38030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T04:52:28.000Z","msg":"full sta